{
  "texts": [
    "The overall accuracy of the whole system is 74.09%.",
    "The limitation of this study is that it uses a fixed window size for NE tags i.e.",
    "a maximum of three words can be considered while matching words for NE tags.",
    "For NEs consisting of more than three words are misclassified as two or more separate NEs.",
    "Another limitation is that the system is unable to handle all date formats."
  ]
}